# ./.GITIGNORE—skipping files, dirs, and patterns—for the monorepo and its libraries/packages
# Using '**/...' ensures these rules apply to all subdirectories.

# General
**/__*__/
**/.*/
**/~*/
**/~*

!**/.vscode/
!**/.git*/
!**/.env/
!**/.config/
!**/.husky/

# Dependencies & Build Artifacts
# Ignore all dependency directories regardless of depth.
**/node_modules/

# Ignore common build and output directories at any level.
**/dist/
**/build/
**/coverage/
**/out/
**/bundle/
**/release/
**/target/
**/pub/


# Logs & Error Files
# Ignore specific dependency manager debug logs. The '*' is to catch
# rotated log files (e.g., 'npm-debug.log.1').
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*
**/pnpm-debug.log*

# OS-Specific Files
# Ignore files generated by various operating systems.
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
*.lnk

# Cache & Temp
*.~*
*~
.eslintcache
*-lock.*
*.lock

**/cache/
*.cache.*
*.cache

**/dump/
*.dump.*
*.dump

**/bak/
*.bak.*
*.bak

**/backup/
*.backup.*
*.backup

**/temp/
*.temp.*
*.temp

**/tmp/
*.tmp.*
*.tmp

**/debug/
*.debug.*
*.debug

**/log/
*.log.*
*.log

**/trace/
*.trace.*
*.trace

**/.turbo/

# Test results
**/reports/
**/*-reports/
**/*_reports/

**/results/
**/*-results/
**/*_results/

**/artifacts/
**/*-artifacts/
**/*_artifacts/

**/analysis/
**/*-analysis/
**/*_analysis/

# Documents
*.md
!**/ADR/*.md
!**/architectur*/*.md
!**/docs/*.md
!**/documentation/*.md
!./*.md
!**/LICENSE
!**/LICENSE.md
!**/README
!**/README.md
!**/CHANGELOG
!**/CHANGELOG.md

# Environment variables
.env
.env.*

# SSH and TLS keys
id_*
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx
*.crt
*.pwd

